Ask the user to enter a number(n1)
Display the available operators(+, -, *, /, %)
Ask the user to enter an operator(op)
Ask the user to enter a number(n2)
IF op = "+" THEN
Display n1 + n2
ELSE
IF op = "-" THEN
Display n1 - n2
ELSE
IF op = "*" THEN
Display n1 * n2
ELSE
IF op = "/" THEN
Display n1 / n2
ELSE
IF op = "%" THEN
Display n1 % n2
ELSE
Display Invalid Operator Entered
